                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10094" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0300</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">390 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多用一根竹，少砍一棵树：新兴家居打造绿色产业链中的东方雅颂</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Using One More Bamboo, Cutting One Less Tree: The Oriental Elegance in the Green Industry Chain of Xinxing Home Furnishings</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">戴永务，余忠，赵诚堃，陈婷婷，孙于岚</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福州新兴家居用品有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色产业链；网络组织治理理论；产业链延伸；价值星系模型；三重底线理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green Industry Chain; Network Organizational Governance Theory; Industrial Chain Extension; Value Constellation; Triple Bottom Line Theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了新兴家居创始人林起恩年轻留学时受竹制品启发，决心打造全竹产业链的过程。产业链上游“公司+农户”模式救活竹林；中游研发与智能制造攻克难题；下游品牌体验打破传统观念，最终实现实现经济、生态、文化效益统一。但新兴家居仍面临国内市场认知、成本及回收等挑战，需要进行持续绿色探索。该案例基于产业链整合、网络组织治理、价值星系等理论，深入展现新兴家居如何通过产业链网络布局实现多主体协同和价值共创，旨在帮助学生感知绿色创新高质量发展阶段下传统竹制家居行业寻求绿色产业链整合与延伸的契机。同时，本文也为相关企业在绿色产业实践中如何应对未来发展挑战、实现可持续发展提供了借鉴和参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the process of Lin Qien, the founder of Xinxing Home Furnishings, who was inspired by bamboo products when he was young and studying abroad, and was determined to build a complete bamboo industry chain. The &quot;company+farmer&quot; model in the upstream of the industrial chain can revive bamboo forests; Midstream R&amp;D and intelligent manufacturing overcome challenges; The downstream brand experience breaks traditional concepts and ultimately achieves the unity of economic, ecological, and cultural benefits. However, Xinxing home furnishings still face challenges in domestic market awareness, cost, and recycling, and require continuous green exploration. This case is based on theories such as industry chain integration, network organizational governance, and value systems, and deeply demonstrates how Xinxing home furnishings can achieve multi-party collaboration and value co-creation through industry chain network layout. The aim is to help students perceive the opportunities for traditional bamboo home furnishings industry to seek green industry chain integration and extension in the stage of high-quality development of green innovation. At the same time, this article also provides reference and guidance for relevant enterprises on how to cope with future development challenges and achieve sustainable development in the practice of green industries.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">网络组织治理的动因；网络组织治理的特点；价值星系模型；三重底线理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
